1. *Zaljubio* sam se u nju na prvi pogled. (I fell in love with her at first sight.)
2. On se *zaljubio* u svoju najbolju prijateljicu. (He fell in love with his best friend.)
3. Kada sam joj rekla da sam se *zaljubila* u nju, ona me je poljubila. (When I told her that I had fallen in love with her, she kissed me.)
4. Ne mogu da verujem da se moj bivši dečko već *zaljubio* u drugu devojku. (I can't believe that my ex-boyfriend has already fallen in love with another girl.)
5. Koliko puta se možeš *zaljubiti* u istu osobu? (How many times can you fall in love with the same person?)
6. Tako je lepo videti kako se tvoj sin *zaljubio* u knjige. (It's so nice to see how your son has fallen in love with books.)
7. Kada su se upoznali, odmah su se *zaljubili* jedno u drugo. (When they met, they immediately fell in love with each other.)
8. Ne znam šta mi je bilo kada sam se *zaljubila* u njega. (I don't know what came over me when I fell in love with him.)
9. Ona se čini kao osoba koja se neće lako *zaljubiti*. (She seems like someone who won't fall in love easily.)
10. Kako da joj kažem da sam se *zaljubio* u nju? (How do I tell her that I've fallen in love with her?)